title: Sarah Culhane
text: Hello and welcome to my webpage! :)

title: About
text:
I am an undergraduate student at Colorado State University studying ecosystem science and sustainability. I grew up in the beautiful state of Arkansas exploring nature, which helped to nurture my love and appreciation for the outdoors.
My technical skills may be green, but my desire for helping nature thrive is strong.

title: CSU Projects
text: In the spring of 2025 I took a Quantitative Reasoning Class based in R. The first assignment was building a website using github (the one you’re on right now!)

title: CSU Projects
text: In the Spring of 2025, I look a Quantitative Reasoning class based in R. I learned how to write code and learned about data science. The first project was building a static users site with Github Pages…the one you’re on now!
